Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.42,0:24:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H84A8C7&}喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.69,0:24:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H736CBF&}喵～
